  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then of course, at that particular time-- 1943, I think, or maybe even sooner-- they, the Germans, were asking to Hungary, they should give out all the ones who are non-citizens, so to speak, who were born somewhere else, which a lot of them were considered Polish citizens, you know?",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took these families and took them over to the other side, you know, [ON-ENGLISH] and those.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't know if you ever heard of the Dnieper, the river?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Dnieper?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dnieper you know, where, you know, they, they did some killings and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in that particular area, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I was a kid at that particular time, didn't-- but we knew about it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because a lot of people, of course, came back, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so it started quite early.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, like I said, different things, you know, like that happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't recall exactly, you know, I mean, details.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, there was-- you know, Jews were put into jail for different things regardless-- you know, false accusations of smuggling and dealing or whatever.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a lot of people, you know, because they might have not-- they hid themselves from not going into, into the military service.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, you know, some Jews were accused of espionage and all that kind of stuff, you know, where they were hauled away.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you know, I mean, this was conversations, you know, which was going on all the time.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
